34:21.197 --> 34:23.958
I was cleaning and I found
this old box of photos.

34:23.992 --> 34:25.891
I took these so long ago.

34:25.925 --> 34:27.720
Makes me feel very nostalgic.

34:27.755 --> 34:29.377
That's cool. Any good ones?

34:29.412 --> 34:31.138
They're all good.
I took them, you know.

34:32.622 --> 34:34.831
Do you remember that day
at the park a few summers ago?

34:35.866 --> 34:37.696
We used to love going
to the park.

34:37.730 --> 34:39.077
Of course, I do.

34:39.111 --> 34:41.009
It's one of the first times
we ever hung out.

34:41.044 --> 34:42.183
I love this picture.

34:42.735 --> 34:43.598
Me, too.

34:47.464 --> 34:49.880
JULIAN: I am getting
kinda hungry.

34:50.467 --> 34:51.330
Are you?

34:51.848 --> 34:53.091
Yeah, I could eat.

34:54.057 --> 34:55.093
What are you thinking?

34:56.094 --> 35:02.307
Um... Maybe... grilled cheese
and some soup.

35:12.420 --> 35:14.733
What are you doing
with that step stool again?

35:14.767 --> 35:16.769
I can't just stop watering
the plants. They'll die.

35:20.635 --> 35:23.845
What? Why do you look
so confused?
I'll be fine.

35:23.880 --> 35:26.986
I'm just... I'm trying to wrap
my head around the fact

35:27.021 --> 35:30.990
that you've literally fallenand you're going to get back up.

35:31.025 --> 35:32.475
Baby steps.

35:32.509 --> 35:35.926
I'm proud of you, babe.
Good job.

35:38.343 --> 35:40.793
-I'll be fine.
-Okay.

35:41.277 --> 35:42.416
Just be careful.

35:44.418 --> 35:46.454
Wait, don't move.
Stay right there.

35:51.045 --> 35:53.634
Hey, try to stay still.

35:54.497 --> 35:56.706
-[CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS]
-[LAUGHS]

35:59.364 --> 36:02.436
Ooh! [SQUEALS]
Oh, my God! [LAUGHING]

36:05.542 --> 36:06.405
[LAUGHS]

36:13.309 --> 36:15.276
-Babe.
-One second.

36:17.313 --> 36:18.831
What are you looking at?
What's going on?

36:20.419 --> 36:22.490
Come on. You know I hate it
when you do this.

36:22.525 --> 36:23.388
What's up?

36:25.079 --> 36:26.460
Seriously, what the hell
is so important?

36:26.494 --> 36:27.840
These are all losers, right?

36:27.875 --> 36:29.221
Why do you play those things?

36:30.084 --> 36:31.534
I mean, you know,
nobody ever wins.

36:32.707 --> 36:34.537
Why do you keep
taking oxycodone?

36:34.571 --> 36:37.229
Because I still have painfrom the crash, and it helps me.

36:37.264 --> 36:39.852
But we're talking
about you right now.

36:39.887 --> 36:43.339
Okay, well, I get anxietyand gambling is a stress relief.

36:43.373 --> 36:44.340
You know, it's fun.

36:44.374 --> 36:45.617
Until the anxiety comes back.

36:45.651 --> 36:47.101
Same thing with you
and the oxycodone.

36:47.135 --> 36:48.206
What is your point?

36:51.036 --> 36:52.279
Never mind.

36:53.728 --> 36:55.834
I guess I just didn't realize
how much you were gambling.

36:55.868 --> 36:57.180
That's all.

36:57.215 --> 37:00.425
Well, don't worry. It's fine.

37:00.459 --> 37:02.323
Okay? I've got it under control.

37:04.083 --> 37:05.395
Now, smile.

37:05.430 --> 37:07.915
Can you just do it
without the flash, please?

37:11.919 --> 37:12.816
Yeah.

37:19.823 --> 37:21.584
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING]

38:07.319 --> 38:12.980
[JULIAN READING]

38:46.254 --> 38:47.911
[HEART BEATING]

38:52.847 --> 38:53.710
JULIAN: Okay.

38:56.955 --> 38:58.336
This isn't so bad.

39:01.753 --> 39:04.100
I'm gonna get
some fresh air and relax.

39:46.591 --> 39:48.006
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

39:50.318 --> 39:51.837
HUNTER: Hey.
Let me in!

39:51.872 --> 39:53.667
-[KNOCKING CONTINUES]
-[WHISPERING] Fuck.

39:53.701 --> 39:56.877
I just... I made a mistake
earlier. I just...

39:57.774 --> 39:59.017
I just wanna make it right.

40:00.225 --> 40:01.088
Please.

40:02.261 --> 40:03.435
[KNOCKING CONTINUES]

40:03.470 --> 40:04.747
HUNTER:
I just wanna
make it right.

40:04.781 --> 40:07.059
Stop banging, Hunter,
or I'm gonna call the police.

40:08.578 --> 40:11.167
Just... I just want
to apologize.

40:11.201 --> 40:12.444
Just let me in.

40:12.479 --> 40:13.790
[CONTINUES KNOCKING]

40:15.689 --> 40:17.656
How the hell do you know
where I live, Hunter?

40:19.624 --> 40:21.764
I don't trust you.
Not after the other day.

40:21.798 --> 40:24.214
HUNTER: I know.
I can't expect you to.

40:24.249 --> 40:25.112
Okay, I just...

40:26.009 --> 40:28.115
I just... I made a mistake.
All right?

40:28.149 --> 40:30.151
I want to apologize.

40:30.186 --> 40:33.534
Just please... Just...
I just want to say I'm sorry,

40:33.569 --> 40:36.537
but I want to say it your face
not this fucking door.

40:48.169 --> 40:50.448
Julian is in the other room
and I do not want him
to see you.

40:50.482 --> 40:51.483
-Okay?
-Okay.

40:51.518 --> 40:53.002
So, if you say
another fucking word,

40:53.036 --> 40:54.141
or make any more noise,

40:54.175 --> 40:55.660
I'm gonna shut this door
and call the fucking police.

40:55.694 --> 40:57.938
Okay, okay.
Just let me in for a second.

40:57.972 --> 41:00.043
You have 60 seconds, Hunter.
What the fuck do you want?

41:00.078 --> 41:01.528
Okay! I just... I just...

41:03.426 --> 41:04.910
I made a mistake earlier, okay?

41:04.945 --> 41:07.430
I didn't mean to ruin
our relationship, all right?

41:07.465 --> 41:09.605
Look, hey, we're friends.

41:09.639 --> 41:11.503
We don't have a relationship.
We never will.

41:11.538 --> 41:12.746
We are not friends.

41:12.780 --> 41:14.782
Yes, we did. See,
that's what I'm talking about.

41:14.817 --> 41:16.543
We did have
a relationship, okay?

41:16.577 --> 41:18.683
-I fucked it up,
-Yeah. Yeah. Okay.

41:19.097 --> 41:20.201
Okay? I'm sorry.

41:20.236 --> 41:21.444
No, it doesn't matter.

41:21.479 --> 41:23.239
Whatever it was,
it's over now, okay?

41:26.967 --> 41:29.141
-Ah!
-Let me in before I break
this fucking door!

41:29.176 --> 41:31.592
You need to leave, Hunter.
This is not fucking okay.

41:31.627 --> 41:32.938
Get the fuck out of here.

41:34.457 --> 41:35.700
[GRUNTS]

42:03.037 --> 42:04.349
I can see you, Hunter.

42:04.383 --> 42:06.593
Just give me some pills,
Liv, all right?

42:07.904 --> 42:08.940
Whole bottle.

42:10.320 --> 42:11.632
And I'll be gone.

42:11.667 --> 42:13.289
Get the fuck out of here, dude.

42:13.323 --> 42:15.809
I'm not going anywhere
until you give me some, Liv.

42:24.611 --> 42:25.819
Okay, listen to me.

42:25.853 --> 42:27.510
Leave now and meet me
on the corner in an hour

42:27.545 --> 42:28.925
and I'll have
some pills for you.

42:29.305 --> 42:30.893
I don't trust you.

42:30.927 --> 42:33.965
I don't trust you either.
But if you have any chance
of getting a fix,

42:33.999 --> 42:35.898
you're going to
leave right now.

42:35.932 --> 42:38.383
All right, but if you don't
show up in an hour,

42:38.417 --> 42:39.660
you know I'm coming back.

42:40.247 --> 42:41.110
I'll be there.

43:07.654 --> 43:08.724
JULIAN: Liv.

43:10.380 --> 43:11.243
Hey.

43:13.936 --> 43:14.799
Olivia.

43:17.042 --> 43:17.905
Liv!

43:20.045 --> 43:20.908
Babe, it's me.

43:25.982 --> 43:26.845
Hey.

43:27.950 --> 43:30.193
Hey, I love you so much.
Don't drive away.

43:30.228 --> 43:31.160
Just wait.

43:31.194 --> 43:32.368
[INAUDIBLE]

43:33.472 --> 43:34.335
JULIAN:
What happened?

43:36.234 --> 43:37.925
[HEART BEATING]

43:52.975 --> 43:53.838
Liv?

44:06.713 --> 44:08.369
This shit
isn't working anymore.

44:16.377 --> 44:17.240
Babe?

44:17.655 --> 44:18.690
Hi.

44:21.520 --> 44:22.383
JULIAN: I missed you.

44:23.971 --> 44:26.698
I'm right here. You okay?

44:27.354 --> 44:29.425
-Yeah, I'm fine.
-Yeah?

44:29.459 --> 44:31.427
-Are you?
-Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.

44:31.461 --> 44:32.324
Don't worry.

44:33.567 --> 44:35.845
I am starving.
Are you hungry yet?

44:35.880 --> 44:37.951
Do you still want
grilled cheese and soup?

44:37.985 --> 44:39.987
-Thousand percent, yes.
-Okay.

44:43.266 --> 44:44.267
Well... [CHUCKLES]

44:44.302 --> 44:48.168
We don't have any cheese
or soup, so that's cool.

44:48.202 --> 44:51.274
I will just run out
and grab some.

44:51.309 --> 44:53.380
Um, do you need anything?

44:53.794 --> 44:55.175
More pills.

44:55.209 --> 44:57.591
This is me holding you
accountable and telling you no.

44:57.625 --> 44:58.730
How many do you have left?

44:58.765 --> 45:00.111
Only a few.

45:00.145 --> 45:02.630
All right. Well, just try
your machine. You'll be fine.

45:02.665 --> 45:04.184
All right? I'll be right back.

45:04.218 --> 45:06.013
Hey, look,
let's just make something else.

45:06.048 --> 45:08.257
I'm just gonna go out
and grab some stuff, okay?

45:09.707 --> 45:10.742
All right.

45:11.812 --> 45:13.952
-See you later.
-See you.

45:34.593 --> 45:36.250
♪ Face up...

45:37.389 --> 45:38.666
[OLIVIA LAUGHING]

45:38.701 --> 45:42.809
♪ Gazing at the ceiling

45:42.843 --> 45:47.123
♪ Game's up
Never bring you down

45:50.989 --> 45:55.062
♪ Face up, our love's

45:55.097 --> 45:59.273
♪ Craving for some feeling

45:59.308 --> 46:04.520
♪ Game's up
We're nowhere to be found

46:07.109 --> 46:11.527
♪ I'm stuck, I'm stuck

46:11.561 --> 46:14.772
♪ I'm stuck here in my skin

46:15.496 --> 46:19.500
♪ I'm stuck, I'm stuck

46:19.535 --> 46:21.986
♪ I'm stuck with you

46:22.020 --> 46:25.023
♪ Tell me it gets easier

46:26.128 --> 46:29.234
♪ Tell me it gets easier

46:30.166 --> 46:33.825
♪ Tell me it gets easier

46:33.860 --> 46:36.517
♪ That I'll figure it out

46:38.554 --> 46:41.315
♪ Tell me it gets easier

46:42.696 --> 46:45.526
♪ Tell me it gets easier...

46:46.458 --> 46:47.183
JULIAN: Liv!

46:47.218 --> 46:49.979
♪ Tell me it gets easier

46:50.600 --> 46:51.463
JULIAN: Liv!

46:53.880 --> 46:55.295
Where are you?

46:56.365 --> 46:58.056
[CRASHING]

47:26.050 --> 47:28.431
Let's not make a scene.
Just fucking hand 'em over.

47:28.466 --> 47:30.433
Listen to me.
You said you made a mistake.

47:30.468 --> 47:32.711
You said you wanted
to make things right, right?

47:32.746 --> 47:34.679
Yeah, I'll make it right.
I will.

47:34.713 --> 47:36.267
Just give me
the fucking pills first.

47:36.301 --> 47:38.890
No more meetups,
no more uninvited visits.

47:38.925 --> 47:40.823
I never want to see you again.

47:40.858 --> 47:41.893
No more visits.

47:44.206 --> 47:46.035
Julian's getting off of these.

47:46.070 --> 47:47.657
OLIVIA:
This is the last
of what I have.

47:47.692 --> 47:49.521
He's got a couple more,

47:49.556 --> 47:51.661
and then he's gonna be done.
And then, this whole entire
thing will be over, okay?

47:51.696 --> 47:53.767
Liv, give me the fucking bottle.

47:53.801 --> 47:54.975
Okay? I'm not gonna
ask again.

47:55.010 --> 47:57.598
Give me the bottle
before I fucking take it!

48:03.535 --> 48:04.398
Go home.

48:05.848 --> 48:06.884
Leave.

48:24.073 --> 48:26.317
[HEART BEATING]

49:28.793 --> 49:29.863
Can I have a glass?

49:29.897 --> 49:30.760
Jesus.

49:32.038 --> 49:33.591
